[^17]: Refer to "3. Concept for Expanding Publication in Machine-Readable Data Formats" and Attachment 2 "Points to Note When Creating Data for Numbers (Tables), Text, and Geospatial Information" in the "Basic Approach to Data Publication by Ministries and Agencies for the Promotion of Secondary Use (Guidelines)".

